      "date": "2015-05-15 02:26:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI think that one and the \"#if LUSTRE_VERSION_CODE < OBD_OCD_VERSION(2, 7, 53, 0)\" in osd-ldiskfs/osd_quota.c are not proper. They are used to migrate old quota amin files into new format. As long as we support upgrading 2.1 system to 2.8, these code can't be removed.\n\nShould I fix this in this patch or in another one?",
